<%- include('../partials/header') %>
<%- include('../partials/navigation') %>

<main class="min-h-screen bg-gradient-to-b from-gray-50 to-white py-24">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 text-center mb-24">
        <span class="inline-block px-4 py-1.5 mb-6 bg-brand-blue/10 text-brand-blue rounded-full text-xs font-black tracking-widest uppercase">
            UK Company Registration Specialists
        </span>
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-8 tracking-tight leading-tight">
            Empowering Global Founders Since 2018
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto font-medium leading-relaxed">
            UK Ltd Registration was established to break down geographic and bureaucratic barriers. We help international and UK-based entrepreneurs incorporate and scale their businesses in the world's most prestigious corporate ecosystem.
        </p>
    </section>

    <!-- Our Story & What We Do -->
    <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 mb-24">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-start">
            <div class="space-y-6 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-gray-900 tracking-tight">Our Founding Story</h2>
                <p>
                    In 2018, our founders—former compliance analysts and corporate secretarial specialists—noticed a widening gap in the startup ecosystem. While the UK Companies House digital registry was theoretically open to all, navigating the regulatory environment was a stressful process for global founders. Ambiguous pricing, hidden fees, complex identity verification mandates under anti-money laundering (AML) laws, and localized tax registration rules frequently stalled legitimate startups.
                </p>
                <p>
                    To solve this, we built a modern, unified corporate formation platform. Our mission was simple: provide a premium, transparent, and completely remote "Business-in-a-Box" solution. By combining real-time API registry links, secure biometric KYC verification, prestigious virtual offices, and proactive compliance alerts, we made it possible for anyone to start a compliant UK Limited company from their laptop in under 6 hours.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-6 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-gray-900 tracking-tight">What We Do</h2>
                <p>
                    As premier **UK company registration specialists**, we handle the entire corporate lifecycle for modern startups, e-commerce sellers, agencies, and remote consultants. We go far beyond basic company filing. We act as your ongoing corporate secretary and compliance officers.
                </p>
                <p>
                    From registered office address hosting in central London to VAT and EORI filing, annual CS01 Confirmation Statement preparation, company name check auditing, and assisted corporate bank account setup, we guarantee 100% peace of mind. We ensure your business is fully aligned with HMRC regulations and the 2026 Economic Crime and Corporate Transparency Act (ECCTA) rules.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Credentials & Trust Signals -->
    <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 mb-24">
