                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1">Edward Sterling</h3>
                <p class="text-brand-blue text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">Founder & Senior Compliance Officer</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed flex-1">
                    Former Companies House senior policy analyst with over 15 years of corporate compliance experience. Edward ensures that all digital workflows satisfy standard anti-money laundering and ECCTA statutory laws.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Team Member 2 -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl border border-gray-100 p-8 shadow-sm flex flex-col items-center text-center">
