                    Sarah specializes in assisting non-resident founders with cross-border taxation, multi-currency banking introductions, and VAT/EORI setups. She has personally overseen the entry of 4,000+ global brands into the UK market.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Team Member 3 -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl border border-gray-100 p-8 shadow-sm flex flex-col items-center text-center">
