                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1">Alistair Vance</h3>
                <p class="text-brand-blue text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">Senior Corporate Secretary</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed flex-1">
                    An expert in statutory record-keeping and corporate governance. Alistair manages the annual CS01 Confirmation Statement audit desk, coordinating shareholder equity reorganizations and PSC restructures.
                </p>
